REFACTORING NOTES:
- Removed duplicate card wrapper CSS (background, backdrop-filter, border, padding, shadow, hover) - now handled by ContentCard
- Removed duplicate icon badge CSS (size, filter, drop-shadow) - now handled by IconBadge
- Removed ~45 lines of CSS
- Kept sidebar accent pattern (unique to this component)
- Kept title and layout styles (component-specific)
- Base components used:
  * IconBadge (variant="accent", size="lg")
  * ContentCard (variant="default", padding="md")
-->
